{"tid":1347214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［進化版左膠］先扮勇武佔領整路障，然後叫人退場散水","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T13:18:24.000Z","uid":40250,"like":29,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"271bbc73a98954601966e1ce28a7bb018d63040e","tid":1347214,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:38:50.000Z","msg":"整路障出黎，最大作用係分隔差佬同示威者，等示威者可以遠攻同對峙。 呢班撚屌set完之後差佬就夾晒時間出黎，之黎班撚屌一人一枝大聲公叫人一二一二咁後退，仲要退到九仗遠。<br />\n<br />\n發覺上次沙田同今次上環，呢班人已經同差佬有共識引示威者係邊到防守，然黎圍捕。<br />\n<br />\n上次沙田明明守緊沙田圍條橋，好地地繼續對峙，示威者就唔會入晒去沙田新城市廣場到。 班左膠以為差佬會守承諾開地鐵俾人走，點知差佬反口結果打巷戰。<br />\n<br />\n今次你地又叫人散水退去守中環，搞到西環班前線俾人孤立。結果差佬金鐘同西環一齊夾。<br />\n<br />\n左膠我屌你老母，你班仆街用盡方法控制群者當d示威者係傻仔亂尻咁點，正一賤種左仔。每個人都有自由意志同民族精神，未有覺悟未有心理準備既人要知道，自己既命運同生死唔可以交托係人地身上。你班死左仔就想盡辦法去蠱惑人心，製造恐慌，洗版控制輿論搞分化。<br />\n<br />\n香港係咁危難既時候你地仲為左自身利益出賣香港人，我屌你老母臭閪！<br />\n<br />\n你話想示威者安全離開，為左示威者好。我屌柒你就係你地呢班撚樣搞到個個出黎示威都唔知自己做緊乜，個個無心理準備又唔買自己裝備。<br />\n搞乜柒物資站派物資，搶撚晒d資源搞到上前線班示威既者無裝備，想買都買唔撚到。<br />\n因為你班柒頭咁樣做，嘥錢嘥時間嘥力，你叫d人點持續落去？ 仆你個街<br />\n<br />\n我同大家講！ 今次去元朗好柒危險，屌你老味唔好再聽班左膠點，自己要有意識出黎想做d乜，有咩目標，自己做好準備。無打算開拖想遊行既就遊完走。想進一步既就要知道自己要點打落去，唔好縮要團結有組織！"},{"pid":"f6f765f73c3be538d9560aa43e4587ecd0ae1d25","tid":1347214,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:39:07.000Z","msg":"推！推！推！"},{"pid":"aba7d0108e80daa4e41e768fa19617f81d11f92d","tid":1347214,"uid":40250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:39:51.000Z","msg":"今時今日左膠未篤灰，因為無人出黎拆佢檔，呢班撚屌好快現形！"},{"pid":"a65e0ea7463dc3ea48e09779b9487f8554481610","tid":1347214,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:40:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"babbadfc37d6e76c9cfbac534d4aa4963649cae8","tid":1347214,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:40:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4cb667a610ec95f37ef5d04fc778ec515bbaf3af","tid":1347214,"uid":128763,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:43:11.000Z","msg":"又玩分化？"},{"pid":"07254a002eef83131c79db010599b20ae3379eb6","tid":1347214,"uid":128763,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:44:32.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 玩脷者(勇闖) )"},{"pid":"95997ecc768330a1cf28d033a7cc9d961e449f5c","tid":1347214,"uid":173179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:44:53.000Z","msg":"做乜鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725fb094134629e34798276e76a934d9f5905c7b","tid":1347214,"uid":114754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:45:55.000Z","msg":"0分<br />\n繼續努力"},{"pid":"f7305d0433d068f7e5295013a93297e73ea00985","tid":1347214,"uid":84323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cb667a610ec95f37ef5d04fc778ec515bbaf3af","tid":1347214,"uid":128763,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:43:11.000Z","msg":"又玩分化？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:45:56.000Z","msg":"今次我撐樓主後半<br />\n屌你地唔上前<br />\n咁厚裝托柒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4553a81db985e20c8e1e92aa5b8bb84f52e4455","tid":1347214,"uid":259302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:49:39.000Z","msg":"咪撚再整路障，嘥力嘥時間，你幾時見過外國衝突整路障？"},{"pid":"f1de20f173201fc3f4ffdcab8551d5d1c62acd58","tid":1347214,"uid":40250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:46:55.000Z","msg":"唔撚岩聽就block?<br />\n<br />\n有上過前線既實明我講咩，保持意志<br />\n警黑合作去到呢個地步，法治崩潰，根本退無可退，已經無叫自己放棄既理由。<br />\n<br />\n繼續默默工作，遊行一係大做，一係行完就算，目的要清楚唔好嘥多餘既力同時間。平日就用盡方法努力儲低資本，應付日後既戰鬥<br />\n<br />\n大家應該互相照應，經濟上精神上都要互助互相支持"},{"pid":"1d7805b0b352410bc6a080ac25351a68d2b3ad34","tid":1347214,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4553a81db985e20c8e1e92aa5b8bb84f52e4455","tid":1347214,"uid":259302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:49:39.000Z","msg":"咪撚再整路障，嘥力嘥時間，你幾時見過外國衝突整路障？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:47:30.000Z","msg":"整黎唔上前峙遠攻，整黎嘥氣"},{"pid":"e807ee9da7e471e97ebef5e646fc9b6954e3c301","tid":1347214,"uid":40250,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:54:35.000Z","msg":"所謂be water係掩飾自己既懦弱<br />\n打都唔敢打，差佬未埋身就走，出咩黎示威"},{"pid":"b4c278668c4b902579cea1e723df8c137012e5fd","tid":1347214,"uid":103936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:58:54.000Z","msg":"1 roadblock 擋近戰<br />\n但狗仔已經唔只近戰 仲會用槍<br />\n頂住都係食子彈<br />\n2 目的唔係佔領<br />\nroadblock 只係隔一隔<br />\n唔通冇驅趕就守到第朝?<br />\n3 目標達成就應該全身而退<br />\nbe water 就係要變<br />\n守住roadblock 同 冇人受傷之間 你會點揀?<br />\n<br />\nsorry 我思維上唔係真勇武"},{"pid":"9c951aae742281ca6c1f223f4a3d4ad3566c850f","tid":1347214,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4c278668c4b902579cea1e723df8c137012e5fd","tid":1347214,"uid":103936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:58:54.000Z","msg":"1 roadblock 擋近戰<br />\n但狗仔已經唔只近戰 仲會用槍<br />\n頂住都係食子彈<br />\n2 目的唔係佔領<br />\nroadblock 只係隔一隔<br />\n唔通冇驅趕就守到第朝?<br />\n3 目標達成就應該全身而退<br />\nbe water 就係要變<br />\n守住roadblock 同 冇人受傷之間 你會點揀?<br />\n<br />\nsorry 我思維上唔係真勇武"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:01:10.000Z","msg":"1.）用槍既話更加要整路障加煙阻視線<br />\n2.）隔條撚咩，無人守住一跨就過嗱<br />\n3.）咁守住沙田同中要目的係咩？ 咁一開波就走喇。<br />\n尋晚擺到明一大班人想同差佬開波，唔係班仆街水撚晒d人過中環，係西環開波就唔會搞到局面咁不利<br />\n<br />\n仲有呀，出得黎就預左危險喇，就係左膠班柒頭一直麻卑d群眾以為打唔還手好撚道德高地好有用，成班柒撚懞連基本防備都無。有基本頭盔，豬咀眼罩護甲加埋盾, 唔出實彈可以傷得去邊？<br />\n<br />\n你連突破心理關口既勇氣都無，仲講乜撚示威<br />\n口硬無撚用，心要夠硬頭腦要清晰先得。<br />\n我見大部份人都死剩把口"},{"pid":"4632052bde7d935ad23beb7edad1a8b2384611dc","tid":1347214,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:32:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87b034e3adc6085fb1780e7aa356082e2258a997","tid":1347214,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aba7d0108e80daa4e41e768fa19617f81d11f92d","tid":1347214,"uid":40250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:39:51.000Z","msg":"今時今日左膠未篤灰，因為無人出黎拆佢檔，呢班撚屌好快現形！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:36:23.000Z","msg":"係，屌你老母現場一隻差佬都無叫人走。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e867d58feb188be5e37c81d4747c93b2256dba","tid":1347214,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:51:04.000Z","msg":"又黎喇，係咁叫人散水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw, 散水都無所謂，屌你老味可唔可以同現場d人單聲，你地同差佬傾左打算點做？ 走到咁撚狼尻狽，又有幾話手足俾人拉左，屌那星<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n次次一叫人散都目到你班泛民囉咪，仆你個街"},{"pid":"c1e8c6cdc1b0ff81dddce4e123e68bd787c7c46d","tid":1347214,"uid":268559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:09:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7320a5eb8704c3d9dc05e55dc9a3d1c8ddfc1c7","tid":1347214,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:13:33.000Z","msg":"仲以為香港到左生死存亡個陣，你班左膠同泛民真心認錯大和解，點撚知都係為左私利，當示威者係棋咁老點"},{"pid":"0f20fffe7e648e5ec76133753cbb652edc113aea","tid":1347214,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:14:36.000Z","msg":"大家出到黎要知自己想做乜，和理非遊行就遊行。想開波就開波，開波就要做好準備，唔好咁易縮"},{"pid":"e64fb6742ce7901f09e33e0f14c3a38b4a4f72fc","tid":1347214,"uid":255030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:18:24.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能"}]}